txt.en: Feathers can be found on birds in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should collect feathers.
A storage crate can be found in either Trader's Wharf or Trestlebridge.\n\nYou should place the feathers in a storage crate.
Place the feathers in a storage crate
Someone has posted a task to collect feathers in the Wildwood.
The bulletin notice reads:\n\n'Needed: Feathers from the Wildwood for craft and trade. You will be rewarded for your efforts.'
